      <title>Weapons of Blight</title>
      <author>Dishman</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/564505</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/564505#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">df167fab9a34fd393c38932c1b940e426ab3183e</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Dec 2024 02:35:18 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b693bd09f6.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b69fe6391f.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b692f8d0bd.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b692fdf27a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b692f86b6e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b692fa5ccb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b693006cc5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b6930130bb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b693085d69.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b6c10cb22b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b6930799bb.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b69304896b.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b693050461.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b69308bae9.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/676b6c023955a.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;Weapons of Blight adds standalone Blight Ganon weapons--Waterblight's spear, Fireblight's greatsword, and Thunderblight's scimitar + &#13;
shield, each with their own attributes;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Spear of Blight&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;- 24 dmg &lt;br&gt;- 55 durability&lt;br&gt;- Frostspear effect&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://i.imgur.com/bcD50t7.png" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Cleaver of Blight&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;br&gt;- 63 dmg&lt;br&gt;- 35 durability&lt;br&gt;- Fires mini fireball projectiles&lt;br&gt;- Hammer effect (Smashes ore deposits, effective against Taluses)&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://i.imgur.com/LvnOzxg.png" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Scimitar of Blight&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;- 35 dmg&lt;br&gt;- 42 durability&lt;br&gt;- Fires thunderball projectiles&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="BlueColor"&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;Shield of Rancor&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;- 45 guard power&lt;br&gt;-&amp;nbsp; 42 durability&lt;br&gt;- Auto reflects Guardian lasers&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://i.imgur.com/yS78se1.png" width="40%"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;All count as ancient weapons, as you'd expect. Craft them at the ancient oven &lt;del&gt;until I feel like implementing a better way to obtain them&lt;/del&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;This is an updated port of my &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/496557"&gt;original Weapons of Blight mod&lt;/a&gt; for the &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/games/6386"&gt;Switch version&lt;/a&gt;, which I made nearly a year ago. Let me know if you find any issues or have any suggestions!&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/weaponsofblight_6131e.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
