    <item>
      <title>Mythra Outfit &amp; blade (Linkle)</title>
      <author>i2m</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/404030</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/404030#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">9dab278bafd6194c956c19e4d44d728fae08a88f</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Dec 2024 22:21:05 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a2d11241.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a30e002e.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a340f6ab.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a3734d22.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a3a363a5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a3cd4ac8.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a3f80a75.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a4227131.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a44f1e75.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a477a624.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a4a2d3fe.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a505e9b5.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a4d5b4ce.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a53a4fb1.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/63336a55b7687.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/6334ca81ed045.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67692d0ec7e11.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Update:&lt;/strong&gt; New hairstyle (fix)&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="color: var(--DefaultGreyColor)"&gt;A very small fix to the previous update.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style="color: var(--DefaultGreyColor)"&gt;Please reinstall &lt;strong&gt;mythra_hairstye_alt.bnp&lt;/strong&gt; if you got it early today.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;Added a new hairstyle with a more classic design, for those who don't like the peculiar Mythra's hair design. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span class="PurpleColor"&gt;Fixed&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class="PurpleColor"&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;Shock protection effect was missing, one part of the tiara's texture was not included. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;The hairstyle can be installed on its own and it's purchasable in the Akkala Ancient Lab.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;INTRODUCTION&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;This mod adds a&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;standalone Mythra Outfit &lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;from&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;Xenoblade 2&lt;/u&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;for&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Linkle&lt;/b&gt;, purchasable in the&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp;Akkala Ancient Tech Lab.&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp;You can also install her &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Aegis Sword&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;b&gt;replacing &lt;/b&gt;the &lt;b&gt;Thunderblade&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This outfit is a variation of the one found in Xenoblade 2, specially tailored for Linkle. It matches most of the features found in my&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/167707"&gt;Pyra Outfit Renewal&lt;/a&gt;, like the&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;HD textures&lt;/b&gt;, the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;glowing&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;effect on&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Emerald Ether Lines&lt;/b&gt;, icons, bump maps, reflection maps, etc. The main differences are, sadly no Zelda's Ballad version, no options for glowing intensity during install, and the outfit is not dyeable.&lt;br&gt;&lt;del&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/del&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/mythra_m01.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;del&gt;&lt;b&gt;Switch&amp;nbsp;version&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;is available&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/404483"&gt;&lt;u&gt;here&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, thanks to&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1874702"&gt;Cod3xDev&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/del&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; Standalone sword only for&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Switch&lt;/b&gt;,&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/431159"&gt;&lt;u&gt;here&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/2487799" class="MemberLink"&gt;hanxiuxxy&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;SETUP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;ul type="square"&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Mythra_Thunder_Dress_v1.bnp&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;OR&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;Mythra_Thunder_Dress_Stockings_v1.bnp&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;Install &lt;b&gt;one&lt;/b&gt; to get the &lt;u&gt;Mythra Outfit&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;for&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;Linkle Mod&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&amp;nbsp;as standalone purchasable&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;item in the Akkala Ancient Tech lab, with&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;or without &lt;b&gt;stockings&lt;/b&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Mythra_Thunder_Blade_v1.bnp&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;(&lt;b&gt;optional&lt;/b&gt;)&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;Install it to get the &lt;u&gt;Mythra Aegis Sword&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;i&gt;replacing the existing &lt;b&gt;Thunderblade&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;There is an alternative long hairstyle (purchasable in the Akkala Ancient lab) that can be installed independently of the whole set, with a more classic design (based on Linkle's Majora's Mask hairstyle):&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;font color="#6ee16c"&gt;&lt;b class="SelectedElement"&gt;Mythra_Hairstyle_alt.bnp&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Only for WiiU.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;EXTRA&lt;/b&gt;: You can install the outfit as a replacement of the Rubber set too:&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Rubber_Replacement_Mythra.bnp&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;WiiU &amp;amp; switch versions&amp;nbsp;by&amp;nbsp;&lt;a class="MemberLink" href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1708955"&gt;Kitsen&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/mythra_m03.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;THANKS &amp;amp; CHANGES&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;To&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/members/1739516"&gt;Sockpoppet&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;for allowing me to use his &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/393291"&gt;Linkle Mythra Cosplay&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;as a base for my mod. I added a lot of changes in the 3D mesh, the textures, and other elements in order to match my existing Pyra Outfit mod, please install the one you like!&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;HD upscaled textures&lt;/b&gt;: Using Artificial Intelligence&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; for crisp lines and clear details.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Normal maps&lt;/b&gt;: Restored and enhanced to give bumps&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; and details to the surfaces.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Specular maps&lt;/b&gt;: Restored and enhanced to get better&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; reflections on metal surfaces.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Renewed 3D mesh&lt;/b&gt;: On some details and object joints.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;High Heels:&lt;/b&gt; Because they look awesome.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Hairstyle&lt;/b&gt;: Shorter, simpler and using Linkle hair color.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;New icons&lt;/b&gt;: Matching the ones used in my Pyra Mod.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Improved metal texture&lt;/b&gt;: Shining!&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Aegis Sword&lt;/b&gt;: Electric effects from the Thunderblade.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;img src="https://files.gamebanana.com/bitpit/mythra_m04.gif"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;&lt;b&gt;Ko-Fi:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;https://ko-fi.com/i2mods&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&amp;nbsp; You can&amp;nbsp;support my works by buying me a&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="https://ko-fi.com/i2mods" target="_blank"&gt;coffee&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/i&gt;:)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span class="RedColor"&gt;OTHER MODS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;ul type="square"&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Makeup&lt;/b&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;earrings&lt;/b&gt;,&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;glasses&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;for Linkle --&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/331562"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Clear Camera UI&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;to take clean shots --&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/296638"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="MsoNormal"&gt;Latest&amp;nbsp;&lt;b&gt;Girly Animation Pack&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;--&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/49763"&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/mythra_thunder_dress_v1.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/mythra_thunder_dress_stockings_v1.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
