    <item>
      <title>Structure Spawner Rod (CONCEPT)</title>
      <author>Gojo the Hobo</author>
      <link>https://gamebanana.com/mods/557680</link>
      <comments>https://gamebanana.com/mods/557680#PostsListModule</comments>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">35b5a01f779095cf87c90f643bfc84e1ecd23c45</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 23 Nov 2024 09:25:16 +0000</pubDate>
      <description>&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67419e9047b13.jpg"/&gt;&lt;img src="https://images.gamebanana.com/img/ss/mods/67419e99ce589.jpg"/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;!!!THIS MOD IS A &lt;u&gt;&lt;span class="GreenColor"&gt;CONCEPT&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt; FOR WHAT IS THEORETICALLY POSSIBLE!!!&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;----------It is &lt;b&gt;NOT &lt;/b&gt;meant for a "serious" playthrough of the game----------&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;u&gt;---I only published this for two reasons:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;1)&lt;/b&gt; to show "what can be done" and give inspiration to anyone who might have a cool idea, and&lt;br&gt;2)&amp;nbsp;because I had fun playing with this rod, so I didn't want it to sit in my files and collect dust.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;b&gt;What does it do?&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;This mod turns boko clubs into rods that throw eggs which spawn structures. The structures do have collision thanks to&amp;nbsp;Arch Leaders'&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/307642"&gt;C-actors!&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;But also, because they have collision, it can be very easy to softlock yourself in an invisible wall (just warp or reload a save to escape).&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;ALSO, the structures do not spawn upright all the time (basically, this occurs when the egg thrown by the rod dies in a position that is not vertical. If the egg thrown by the rod dies at a 45 degree angle, then the structure will spawn at that same angle)&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Also, this mod uses content from my other mod &lt;a href="https://gamebanana.com/mods/490630"&gt;CATS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Modder jargon:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="Spoiler SelectedElement"&gt;Long story short, this mod functions by having a rod throw an actor with 1hp (the egg). When the egg breaks, it drops a 0hp shield actor. That 0hp shield actor instantly dies and drops 1 of 15 npcs. Each of those npcs has a different structure's name used in its RideHorseName entry (which is located in the gparam).&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Because each of the structures are spawned from the npc's RideHorseName instead of a droptable, the structures will not despawn because they avoid the drop limit. (This, of course, does mean that you will need to reload the area in order for them to despawn because there will not be a way to destroy the structures)&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Hope this can inspire someone to make a cool idea, or at least give someone a few minutes of fun!&lt;br&gt;&lt;del&gt;Probably shouldn't have released this mod but ahh screw it who cares&lt;/del&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <media:content url="https://files.gamebanana.com/mods/structure_spawner_rod_concept.bnp" type="application/octet-stream"/>
      <category>Other/Misc</category>
      <category>Other/Misc</category>
    </item>
